NK cells with adhesion defects and reduced cytotoxic functions are associated with a poor prognosis in multiple myeloma

This is the repository related to the scRNAseq analysis from Blanquart et al, Blood, 2024

  • you can find all scripts related to the analysis on https://github.com/ImmuneAxisa/NKcell_dysfunction_MM_Blood24
  • the scripts with intermediate analysis files on Zenodo
  • You can browse an illustrative initial exploratory analysis of the dataset here
  • You can browse the advanced analysis of the dataset, used to build the manuscript figures here
